Stable isotope data for lake trout, dreissenids (pelagic baseline), and amphipods (benthic baseline) used in two source model

baseline_2_iso.Rd

Stable isotope data (SIA) for \(\delta\)\(^1\)\(^3\)C and \(\delta\)\(^1\)\(^5\)N for lake trout collected from an ecoregion in Lake Ontario. Values of \(\delta\)\(^1\)\(^3\)C and \(\delta\)\(^1\)\(^5\)N for a pelagic baseline (dreissenids; c1 and n1) and a benthic baseline (amphipods; c2 and n2).

Usage

baseline_2_iso

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 14 rows and 5 columns.
